text: Irina Zuykova (30 May 1958 - 25 December 2010) was a Soviet equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Soviet female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Unified Team Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
